FBIS4-36803 "drnes114_j_94007" FBIS-NES-94-114 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Denies Northern Forces Near al-Mukalla Aden Denies Northern Forces Near al-Mukalla EA1306095394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 2030 GMT 12 Jun 94 EA1306095394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 2030 GMT 12 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A responsible military source at the Defense Ministry of the Democratic Republic of Yemen has categorically denied media reports on the battle within the Shabwah-Hadramawt Axis claiming that the northern forces have reached a point 55 km from al-Mukalla town. The source said these reports are totally untrue. [passage omitted]
